	body id="skrollr-body"
		#main-container
			.grey-overlay.animated.fadeIn
				.row.content-1
					.col-md-12.text-center
						h2.sofia.boldest.fs350 Order yourself a delicious Grub online!
				.container#buttons
					.row
						.col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
							= link_to "Order now",restaurants_path, class: "btn order-now-btn btn-outline btn-block "
					.row
						.col-md-3
							.btn.btn-primary
							  = link_to  "",user_facebook_omniauth_authorize_path, class: "fa fa-facebook-square fa-2x white", id: 'sign_in'
							  p Log in With Facebook
						.col-md-3
						  -if user_signed_in?
							h2#logout
								= link_to "Log Out", destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete, class: "btn btn-danger"


		.fluidbanner data-150="opacity:1;" data-750="opacity:1;"


		.steps.whitebgg

			.step-flex
				.step-flex-items data-150="opacity:1;" data-750="opacity:1;"
					.thumb.text-center
						img src='/assets/pav-bhaji.png' width="50%"
					.content-step.text-center
						p.head.pos Choose your Grub
						p.posp  Sign up & flip through a menu of dishes from restaurants available for delivery around SRM, KTR. We make it simple for you to find just what you're craving.

				.step-flex-items data-150="opacity:1;" data-750="opacity:1;"
					.thumb.text-center.tops2
						img src='/assets/canopy.png' width="50%"
					.content-step.text-center
						p.head.sos Skip the Store
						p.sosp	We have partnered with your favourites around here, so we save you a visit to their store at the very convenience of a few clicks, while they prepare & carefully pack your grub, once you've placed an order.

				.step-flex-items data-150="opacity:1;" data-750="opacity:1;"
					.thumb.text-center.tops1
						img src='/assets/bell.png' width="35%"
						<br>
					.content-step.text-center.pading
						p.head	Ding-Dong!
						p.dosp Bell? Please take the door! Pay your checkout amount to the delivery boy & enjoy your grub! We think long & hard about this whole process so you don't have to. If you like what you eat, you can always share the love or ask us a question!

